<section class="machinery">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Machinery & Production Systems</h2>
    <div class="machinery-content fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
      <p class="machinery-intro">
        Throughout my career, I have operated and managed advanced print and finishing equipment,
        ensuring high-precision output and efficient production workflows.
      </p>

      <div class="machinery-grid">
        <div class="machinery-category">
          <h3>Printing Equipment</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Epson SureColor S60600 (Eco-Solvent)</li>
            <li>Roland VersaCAMM RA-640 & RF-640</li>
            <li>HP Latex Series</li>
            <li>Mimaki Eco-Solvent Series</li>
            <li>Mimaki UVJ Series (UV Printing System)</li>
            <li>Roland LEF-200 UV Flatbed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="machinery-category">
          <h3>Cutting & Finishing Equipment</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Graphtec FC9000 Series</li>
            <li>Jaguar Vinyl Cutter (Flatbed Series)</li>
            <li>Laser Cutting Machine (Acrylic & Sign Fabrication)</li>
            <li>Lamination & Finishing Systems</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="machinery-category">
          <h3>Workflow & RIP Systems</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>ONYX RIP Software</li>
            <li>Caldera VisualRIP</li>
            <li>Color Calibration & Profiling Tools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .machinery {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .machinery-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .machinery-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .machinery-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .machinery-category h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .machinery-category ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .machinery-category li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .machinery-intro {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .machinery-category h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .machinery-category li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
